<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>Welcome to GearX</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #333;
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .header {
                text-align: center;
                padding: 20px 0;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #6366f1;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 20px 0;
            }
            .footer {
                text-align: center;
                padding: 20px 0;
                color: #666;
                font-size: 0.9em;
                border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            }
            .button {
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                background-color: #6366f1;
                color: white;
                text-decoration: none;
                border-radius: 5px;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to GearX!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{ recipientName }},</p>
            
            <p>Welcome to GearX - your ultimate destination for premium gaming gear! We're thrilled to have you join our community of passionate gamers.</p>
            
            <p>With your new account, you can:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Browse our extensive collection of gaming peripherals</li>
                <li>Save your favorite items to your wishlist</li>
                <li>Track your orders easily</li>
                <li>Get exclusive access to special deals and promotions</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>Start exploring our collection today:</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{ url('home') }}" class="button">Visit GearX</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent by GearX. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} GearX. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html> 